parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to accelerate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or jumps out of gear
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission overheats
the vehicle jerks or hesitates when accelerating
the transmission makes a whining or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission overheating can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or fail to accelerate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission overheating light comes on
the vehicle loses power
the transmission slips or jumps out of gear
the vehicle stalls or hesitates when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of power or acceleration can cause the vehicle to stall, hesitate, or fail to respond to driver input, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the vehicle hesitates or stalls when accelerating
the transmission slips or jumps out of gear
the vehicle fails to respond to driver input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the subframe can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to potential loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: Loud thumping noise when applying brakes or driving over bumps
rust holes in the subframe
rusted lower control arm
rusted crossmember
rusted engine cradle
rusted rear suspension lower control arm
rusted brackets holding the subframe
rusted differential
and loud friction noise from the wheel bearing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of airbags and seatbelts can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag warning indicator illuminates
airbags do not deploy in an accident
seatbelts do not lock or malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delayed or unavailable repair parts for the Takata recall can leave vehicles in an unsafe condition, increasing the risk of injury or death in an accident.
symptoms: No parts available for recall repair
long wait times for repair
manufacturer exceeds reasonable time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure to Notify or Delayed Notification of Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to notify vehicle owners of a recall can lead to continued use of a potentially unsafe vehicle, increasing the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: No notification of recall
delayed notification of recall
lack of information on recall status.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion or rust of the subframe can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to potential accidents or injuries. The failure of the subframe can also result in costly repairs.
symptoms: Abnormal sounds
clunking noises
or vibrations while driving
uneven tire wear
rust or corrosion visible on the subframe
and warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The power steering leak can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, leading to potential accidents or injuries.
